    <body>
      <div type="book">
        <linkGrp type="notes"/>
        <div n="Y09C71H1">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-Y09C71H1-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y09C71H1-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y09C71H1-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">&#13;</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-Y09C71H1-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y09C71H1-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y09C71H1-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-Y09C71H1-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y09C71H1-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y09C71H1-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">Y</hi>E people of <hi rend="italics">Ireland</hi>, both country and city,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-2" n="2">Come listen with patience, and hear out my ditty.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-3" n="3">At this time I'll chuse to be wiser than witty.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-4" n="4">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which nobody can deny</hi>/hi&gt;.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-5" n="5">The Half-pence are coming, the nation's undoing,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-6" n="6">There's an end of your ploughing, and baking, and brewing;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-7" n="7">In short, you must all go to rack and to ruin.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-8" n="8">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-9" n="9">Both high men and low men, and thick men and tall men,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-10" n="10">And rich men and poor men, and free men and thrall men,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-11" n="11">Will suffer, and this man, and that man, and all men.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-12" n="12">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-13" n="13">The Soldier is ruin'd, poor man, by his pay,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-14" n="14">His five pence will prove but a farthing a day,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-15" n="15">For meat, or for drink, or he must run away.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-16" n="16">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-17" n="17">When he pulls out his two pence, the Tapster says not,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-18" n="18">That ten times as much he must pay for his shot;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-19" n="19">And thus the poor soldier must soon go to pot.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-20" n="20">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-21" n="21">If he goes to the Baker, the Baker will huff,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-22" n="22">And twenty pence have for a two penny loaf,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-23" n="23">Then, Dog, Rogue, and Rascal, and so kick and cuff.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-24" n="24">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-25" n="25">Again, to the market whenever he goes,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-26" n="26">The Butcher and Soldier must be mortal foes,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-27" n="27">One cuts off an ear, and the other a nose.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-28" n="28">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-29" n="29">The Butcher is stout, and he values no Swagger,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-30" n="30">A Cleaver's a match any time for a Dagger,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-31" n="31">And a blue sleeve may give such a cuff as may stagger.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-32" n="32">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-33" n="33">The Beggars themselves will be broke in a trice,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-34" n="34">When thus their poor farthings are sunk in their price;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-35" n="35">When nothing is left, they must live on their lice.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-36" n="36">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-37" n="37">The Squire, possess'd of twelve thousand a year,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-38" n="38">O Lord! what a mountain his rents would appear!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-39" n="39">Should he take them, he would not have house-room I fear.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-40" n="40">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-41" n="41">Though at present he lives in a very large house,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-42" n="42">There would then not be room in it left for a mouse;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-43" n="43">But the Squire's too wise, he will not take a souse.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-44" n="44">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-45" n="45">The Farmer, who comes with his rent in this Cash,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-46" n="46">For taking these counters, and being so rash,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-47" n="47">Will be kick'd out of doors, both himself and his trash.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-48" n="48">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-49" n="49">For in all the leases that ever we hold,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-50" n="50">We must pay our rent in good Silver and Gold,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-51" n="51">And, not in brass tokens of such a base mold.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-52" n="52">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-53" n="53">The wisest of Lawyers all swear, they will warrant</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-54" n="54">No money but Silver and Gold can be current;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-55" n="55">And since they will swear it, we all may be sure on't.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-56" n="56">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-57" n="57">And I think, after all, it would be very strange,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-58" n="58">To give current money for base in exchange,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-59" n="59">Like a fine lady swapping her moles for the mange.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-60" n="60">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-61" n="61">But read the King's patent, and there you will find,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-62" n="62">That no man need take them but who has a mind,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-63" n="63">For which we must say that his Majesty's kind.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-64" n="64">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-65" n="65">Now God bless the <hi rend="italics">Drapier</hi> who open'd our eyes!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-66" n="66">I'm sure, by his Book, that the Writer is wise,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-67" n="67">He shews us the cheat from the end to the rise.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-68" n="68">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-69" n="69">Nay, farther he shews it a very hard case,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-70" n="70">That this Fellow <hi rend="italics">Wood</hi>, of a very bad race,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-71" n="71">Should of all the fine gentry of <hi rend="italics">Ireland</hi> take place.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-72" n="72">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-73" n="73">That he and his Half-pence should come to weigh down</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-74" n="74">Our subjects so loyal and true to the Crown;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-75" n="75">But I hope, after all, that they will be his own.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-76" n="76">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-77" n="77">This Book, I do tell you, is writ for your goods,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-78" n="78">And a very good Book against Mr. <hi rend="italics">Wood's</hi>;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-79" n="79">If you stand true together, he's left in the suds.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-80" n="80">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which</hi>/hi&gt;, c.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-81" n="81">Ye Shop-men and Trades-men and Farmers, go read it,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-82" n="82">For I think in my soul at this time that you need it,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-83" n="83">Or egad, if you don't, there's an end of your credit.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y09C71H1-line-84" n="84">
              <space><hi rend="italics">Which nobody can deny</hi>/hi&gt;.</space>
            </l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
